    <ComparisonTable columns={costColumns} rows={costRows} />

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">The Regime Forfettario (Flat Tax)</h3>

    <p class="mb-4">
      Italy offers freelancers an attractive flat-rate tax regime called Regime Forfettario. If you qualify, you pay a flat 15% tax on income (or just 5% for your first 5 years as a new activity). This replaces the progressive income tax rates that can reach 43%.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Regime Forfettario Benefits:</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
        <li>• <strong>Tax rate:</strong> 5% for first 5 years, then 15%</li>
        <li>• <strong>Income limit:</strong> Up to €85,000/year revenue</li>
        <li>• <strong>No VAT:</strong> You don't charge or pay VAT</li>
        <li>• <strong>Simplified accounting:</strong> Much less bookkeeping required</li>
        <li>• <strong>INPS still applies:</strong> Social security (~26%) is separate</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

